        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>Stranger Things is a science fiction horror television series created by the Duffer Brothers. The show is set in the 1980s in the town of Hawkins, Indiana, and follows a group of kids who encounter mysterious government experiments, alternate dimensions, and terrifying monsters.</p>
