    <section id="characters" class="section">
        <h2>Characters</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Eleven - A girl with psychokinetic abilities.</li>
            <li>Mike Wheeler - A leader of the group of kids.</li>
            <li>Dustin Henderson - A smart and fun-loving boy.</li>
            <li>Lucas Sinclair - A skeptical but loyal friend.</li>
            <li>Will Byers - A boy who gets trapped in the Upside Down.</li>
            <li>Jim Hopper - The chief of police in Hawkins.</li>
            <li>Joyce Byers - A determined mother who will do anything to protect her sons.</li>
            <nli>Nancy Wheeler - A brave and resourceful teenager who seeks the truth</li>
        </ul>
